
# Flask CI/CD Pipeline Assignment

## Project Description

This project demonstrates CI/CD automation for a Python Flask web application using both Jenkins and GitHub Actions.

Repository used:

https://github.com/mohanDevOps-arch/flask_Practice.git

Forked repository:

https://github.com/<your-github-username>/flask_Practice.git

---

## Part 1: Jenkins CI/CD Pipeline

### Objective

The Jenkins pipeline automates the following stages:

1. Build
2. Test
3. Deploy to staging
4. Email notification

---

## Jenkins Pipeline Stages

### 1. Build

The build stage creates a Python virtual environment and installs required dependencies using pip.

```bash
python3 -m venv venv
. venv/bin/activate
pip install --upgrade pip
pip install -r requirements.txt
